name: caniuse-db
description: Raw browser/feature support data from caniuse.com
readme:
This repo contains raw data from the caniuse.com support tables. It serves two purposes: 1. The ability for anyone interested to update or add to the support data on the site. If you are interested in this, please read the [CONTRIBUTING file](CONTRIBUTING.md). 2. Access to the site's data for other projects. For this use the [data.json](data.json) file which includes all support data. The data in this repo is available for use under a CC BY 4.0 license (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/). For attribution just mention somewhere that the source is caniuse.com. If you have any questions about using the data for your project please contact me here: http://a.deveria.com/contact Thanks, Alexis Deveria
http://caniuse.com
